1. Ja *priznajem* da sam pogrešio. (I admit that I was wrong.)
2. On *priznaje* da mu nedostaješ. (He admits that he misses you.)
3. Ti *priznaješ* da si kriv. (You admit that you are guilty.)
4. Oni *priznaju* svoju grešku. (They admit their mistake.)
5. Da li ćeš *priznati* da si pogrešio? (Will you admit that you were wrong?)
6. Ona je *priznavala* da joj nedostaje dom. (She used to admit that she missed her home.)
7. Kada ćeš *priznati* da si prekršio pravila? (When will you admit that you broke the rules?)
8. Mi smo *priznavali* da smo previše samouvereni. (We used to admit that we were too confident.)
9. Ti si *priznao* svoju grešku, ali to nije dovoljno. (You admitted your mistake, but that's not enough.)
10. Oni *priznajući* svoju krivicu, odlučili su da se iskupi. (By admitting their guilt, they decided to make amends.)